"- topic/keyword " otherprops="g.signal.name">nPMUIRQ</keyword>     signal when the PMU generates an interrupt. </desc></link><link class="- topic/link " format="dita" href="joh1440673951565.xml" role="child" scope="local" type="reference"><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Exporting PMU events</linktext><desc class="- topic/desc ">Some of the PMU events are exported to the ETM trace unit to be     monitored.</desc></link></linkpool></linkpool></related-links></reference>